{
  "id": "69c0276a4693542e3580c38a",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:橋を架ける",
  "created": 1774200705,
  "updated": 1774200720,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c0276a4693542e3580c38a",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:橋を架ける",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200705,
      "updated": 1774200705
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027800000000000b9022c",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200705,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9022d",
      "text": "「はいはーい！今日は“[橋を架ける]”ってテーマでゆるっと鼎談やってくよ〜。なんか壮大じゃね？w でもまあ、ゲームでも橋って大事じゃん？進めるかどうかの分岐ポイント的な」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9022e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9022f",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90230",
      "text": "「ええ、とても象徴的な言葉ですわね。“橋”というのは、隔てられていたもの同士を結びつける…そのような優しい営みのように感じられます。人と人のあいだにも、目には見えぬ橋があるのかもしれません」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90231",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90232",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90233",
      "text": "「定義を整理する。“橋を架ける”は物理的にはインフラ構築、抽象的には関係性の接続。後者はコミュニケーションや信頼構築に該当する。両者に共通するのは“断絶の解消”だ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90234",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90235",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90236",
      "text": "「おお〜、りかちゃん急にガチ解説きたw でもわかる、それ。“断絶の解消”ってなんか強キャラ感ある」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90237",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90238",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90239",
      "text": "「強い言葉ではありますが、確かに本質を突いている気がいたします。断たれていたものが、再びつながる…それは、どこか心が温かくなる出来事ですわね（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9023a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9023b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9023c",
      "text": "「ただし、橋は設計を誤ると崩落する。信頼も同様。根拠のない期待や、過剰な依存はリスクが高い」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9023d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9023e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9023f",
      "text": "「え、なにそれ人間関係も耐久値あるってこと？HPゼロでゲームオーバー的な？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90240",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90241",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90242",
      "text": "「概念的には近い。心理学では“信頼の蓄積”が関係維持に重要とされる。小さな約束を守ることが、橋の強度を上げる要素になる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90243",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90244",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90245",
      "text": "「まあ…それはとても美しい考え方ですわね。一つひとつの言葉や行いが、橋の石となって積み重なってゆく…そう思うと、日々の振る舞いがいっそう大切に思えてまいります」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90246",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90247",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90248",
      "text": "「なんか急に詩的でエモいんだが…！でも確かにさ、“ちょっとしたこと”ってデカいよね。既読スルーしないとか、ちゃんと返事するとかw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90249",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9024a",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9024b",
      "text": "「その例は適切。レスポンスの一貫性は信頼形成に寄与する。デジタル空間における橋とも言える」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9024c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9024d",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9024e",
      "text": "「現代ならではの橋ですわね。目には見えなくとも、確かにそこに存在している…。けれど、ときにすれ違いも起きてしまうのが、少し切ないところです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9024f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90250",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90251",
      "text": "「わかる〜！テキストだけだと誤解バグ起きがちw “え、怒ってる？”みたいな」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90252",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90253",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90254",
      "text": "「それは情報量の不足によるもの。非言語情報が欠落しているため、解釈の幅が広がる。対策としては、意図を明示すること。絵文字や補足も有効」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90255",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90256",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90257",
      "text": "「まあ、心を添える工夫ですのね。言葉だけでは伝えきれぬものを、そっと補うような…（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90258",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90259",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9025a",
      "text": "「まとめると〜、“橋を架ける”ってのは、人と人のあいだをつなぐこと！で、そのためには小さい積み重ねと、ちょい工夫が大事って感じ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9025b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9025c",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9025d",
      "text": "「要点を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9025e",
      "text": " 1. 橋は断絶を解消する手段",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b9025f",
      "text": " 2. 信頼は小さな行動の蓄積で構築される",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90260",
      "text": " 3. 誤解を減らすには情報の補完が必要",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90261",
      "text": "以上だ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90262",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90263",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90264",
      "text": "「とても分かりやすいまとめですわ。橋を架けるという行為は、思いやりと誠実さのかたちなのかもしれませんね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90265",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90266",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027810000000000b90267",
      "text": "「いい感じにまとまったじゃん！なんか今日ちょっと賢くなった気がするw 次はどんなテーマいく〜？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200706,
      "updated": 1774200706
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027840000000000b90268",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200708,
      "updated": 1774200708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027840000000000b90269",
      "text": "#2026-03-23",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200708,
      "updated": 1774200720
    },
    {
      "id": "69c027870000000000b9026a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200712,
      "updated": 1774200712
    }
  ]
}